            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic Sarracina quiescit in pa<lb break="no" n="2"/>ce <expan><abbr>qua</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><ex>v</ex><abbr>ixit</abbr></expan> annos p&amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;(us) <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>inus</ex></expan> XXXI<lb break="no" n="3"/>IIII filii titulum po<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>suerun</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung dreier Arkaden. In der mittleren steht eine Rosette, in beiden anderen ein Baum.</p>
            </div>
